That has been their policy for quite a while.  You can probably
reactivate a receiver on the original account, but if it is a different
account, a new card is required.  Check the &quot;upgrade equipment&quot; section
of http://www.directv.com .  You may be eligible for a new receiver for
free (or a shipping charge).
